<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551596>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1. Representatives of Membracoidea: (A) Mapuchea chilensis (Nielson) (Myerslopiidae), Chile; (B) Mesargus sp. (Cicadellidae: Ulopinae), China; (C) Evacanthus sp. (Cicadellidae: Evacanthinae), China, using hind legs with rows of enlarged setae to spread brochosomes over wing surfaces; (D) Aetalion reticulatum (Linnaeus), (Aetalionidae), adult female guarding egg mass; (E) Melizoderes osborni (Funkhouser); (F) Notocera sp. (Membracidae), Brazil." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4551596/files/figure.png" .

